# Internal: coverage artifacts and large test reports.
# Internal: compiled test output (out/test) — runtime only needs out/src.
out/test/**
coverage/**
.nyc_output/**
dali_preview_report/**
Docs/**
docs/**
# Internal: shell scripts and CI helpers — not needed at runtime.
install.sh
.c8rc.json
# Internal: prior VSIX builds.
*.vsix
# Internal: ad-hoc research packs — kept on disk but never shipped in the VSIX.
*.research-pack.json
# Internal: sibling tools / untracked experiment dirs that live in the working
# tree but are NOT part of the extension — vsce would otherwise bundle them
# (e.g. dali-ui-preview-cli was ~46 MB of unrelated CLI source). samples/ is now
# test-fixtures only — the runtime ships the guided tour under examples/ instead
# (Open Examples), so exclude samples/ wholesale.
dali-ui-preview-cli/**
samples/**
hello-dali.preview.dali.cpp
dali-animation-playground.html
